name: Bernyanyi Menunggu - Halte Rumahsakit
description:
Bernyanyi Menunggu is the first single from Indonesian indiepop Rumahsakit in their last album with the first vocalist-Andri Lemes. Rumahsakit (literally translated as hospital) is first famous in mid-90s. The idea of this work is a twist from the song title, waiting in front of hospital. Yellow-Kuning is one of Rumahsakit single in their second album, Nol Derajat. The round shape is represent the eternal value of Rumahsakit's best era in their fans' mind.
